math-status-introduction:
tina kasabelih paazih mahizaay mawawah a asip-subana’ mizunga {{PLURAL:$1|muse}} cesyun.

isasa’say mikulitay a {{PLURAL:$1|muse}} mawawah tu:
math-test-end: mizunga muse ''$1'' a zikuzan mitanam malaheci tuway
math-test-start: mileku mizunga muse ''$1'' a zikuzan mitanam
math-test-contains-diff: maminay tu sulisulitan $1 caay yamalyilu talaayaway mazateng a sulisulitan $2
math-test-equals-diff: maminay tu sulisulitan $1 caykalecad talaayaway mazateng sulisulitan $2.
mw_math_mathml: MathML pisaungay SVG saca PNG pahalhal (patahkal nizateng tu nu ayzaay saazihay-sakaluk atu saedap a sakaluk)
